.TH SHOAL-DOCTOR 1 "July 2026" "Shoal 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
shoal-doctor \- diagnose a Shoal installation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B shoal-doctor
.RI [ \-\-json ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Checks platform support, paths, permissions, configuration, sandboxing, and companion executables.
It exits nonzero when required checks fail.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-json
Emit a machine-readable report.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shoal (1)
